<h1>About LOTRO Deed freak</h1>
<section>
  <h2>How to use:</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Create an account + main character</li>
    <li>Browse through the deeds and click the ones you completed. They will be highlighted.</li>
    <li>Click on your characters name in the menu to get an overview of your progress.</li>
  </ol>
  <h2>Suggestions</h2>
  <p>You have suggestions or missing deeds/faulty information.
    <form method="post">
